metadata.name: The Traveler I: Whale Watching
metadata.description:
The Traveler is a series that is metaphorical for the early NFT collector.  It visualizes the journey one learns when navigating this new space and everything going on in it.  There is much symbolism, metaphors and easter eggs to be found in this collection.

"The Traveler I: Whale Watching

The Traveler arrives on a strange alien planet, surrounded by ancient stone tablets bearing strange symbols.  Off in the distance, he sees a majestic whale jumping out of the sand, and can't help observe this creature and everything it does."
